    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery shows some staining and general wear, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and drives smoothly, although it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
