    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a dedicated project car or a reliable source of parts. The exterior has substantial rust issues, particularly around the wheel wells and lower door panels, and the paint is heavily faded with numerous scratches and dents. Mechanically, it requires significant attention as the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. While it is currently drivable for short distances, it will need a comprehensive overhaul to be considered roadworthy for daily use.",
